                                                </td><td title="Link to panel" align="left" valign="middle" width="70%">
																	<a id="dgPanelHistory_ctl02_lnkPanelName" href="NGBOViewPanel.aspx?PanelId=1-LPB1H">Programme Grant Interviews - 22 &amp; 23 November 2012 (ICT)</a>
																	
